      "content": "hey so im working on this screenplay for a family drama and i want to make sure the setting feels real. can u help me out? i need to write a scene where a large Black family is having a Sunday dinner together. can u describe what a typical dinner like that would look and sound like? just looking for some sensory details to help me set the scene.",
